”一类之意。据信猎奇一词被大量引用，出自日本ACG的18禁的猎奇杀人（猎奇杀人）类型的虚构作品，对于此种类型的简称。\r\n概要与用法\r\n　　在ACG界中，猎奇可指任何血腥、暴力而残酷的事物，并作为形容词使用，\r\n此外，猎奇也可被当作动词使用。以人为主词时，通常作被动语态，例如：“某角色被猎奇了”；以事为主词，则主要用主动语态，", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "1742": {"data": {"tag_id": 1742, "tag_name": "生活", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "11651": {"data": {"tag_id": 11651, "tag_name": "中考", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 0, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "10058": {"data": {"tag_id": 10058, "tag_name": "挑战", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 0, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 2}, "113843": {"data": {"tag_id": 113843, "tag_name": "抽象", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 0, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 2}, "11617": {"data": {"tag_id": 11617, "tag_name": "马", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 0, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_cou